verbose_text: In order to conduct the test between different FB levels and Noyes ' grading (to have a statistically sufficient number of data in different groups, i.e.,> 6), the femoral arthroscopic score 2 (FAS2) was established by dividing the FAS1 into groups by ranges as follows : grade 0, 0; grade 1, 1-6; grade 2, 7-12; grade 3, 13-18.
